**Subject:** Switched auth provider from Auth0 to Clerk

**Body:**

We're migrating away from Auth0 because of pricing at the next tier. Clerk's
session model is compatible enough that the public `/api/session` contract
does not change. Payments will see no behaviour change; the only thing that
moves is the JWT issuer claim.

**Decision refs:** ADR-014

**Action requested:** None — this is FYI plus a decision broadcast. Payments
should update their shared-index snapshot on next resume.

